721605f-a.title: Manhattan: Marble Hill Avenue - 225th Street (West)
721605f-a.text:
No. 1-11 Marble Hill Ave., at the N.W. corner of West 225th Street.
This structure also bears Nos. 121-129 on the latter street.
About 1929.
Knickerbocker Photo Service.
